name: Awakening of the Queer Pheasant
description:
I had AI dream of a Photoshopped love note I sent to my ex, which hilariously outputted a snake-looking creature. I cropped and brought out as many colors in that as I could to a Lisa Frank level of color saturation. I style merged that with a light corrected photo of my taxidermy pheasant. Then one more time through a small short dream giving me a rainbow pheasant surrounded by eyes, and not surrounded by eyes. From there it was simply figuring out how to get them to blink.
   I dunno, I thought this was really fun to make. In the Deep Dream community running the photos through the AI with no paid for membership takes 6 hours to charge points to do. I could only... Dream... To one day have making art like this worth doing a paid membership to the service.
